quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"So succeeded/followed from after them a succession , they lost/wasted/destroyed the prayers, and they212followed the lusts/desires/cravings, so they will/shall meet/find misguidance/failure"
  19,60,"Except who repented and believed and made/did correct/righteous deeds, so those, they enter the Paradise, and they are not being caused injustice to/oppressed a thing"
  19,61,"Treed gardens/paradises (as) eternal residence which the merciful promises His worshippers/slaves with the unseen/hidden , that He truly, His promise was/is coming (E)"
  19,62,"They do not hear/listen in it nonsense/senseless talk , except (a) greeting/safety/peace and for them, (is) their provision in it (at) daybreaks/early mornings and (at) evening/first darkness/dinnertime"
  19,63,That (is) the paradise which We make inherit (to) who was fearing and obeying from Our worshippers/slaves
  19,64,"And We do not descend except with your Lord`s order/command, for Him what (is) between Our hands, and what (is) behind Us, and what (is) between that, and your Lord was not frequently forgetting"
  19,65,"The skies`/space`s and the earth`s/Planet Earth`s and what (is) between them (B)`s Lord, so worship Him, and endure patience to His worshipping, do you know (an) equivalent to Him"
  19,66,"And the human/mankind says: \"Is (it that) if I died, I will/shall (E) be brought out alive! .\"(expression of wonderment)"
  19,67,Or does not the human remember that We created him from before and (he) was not a thing
  19,68,"So by your Lord We will gather them (E), and the devils, then We will present/bring them (E) around Hell kneeling/standing on (their) toes"
  19,69,Then We will remove (E) from every group/party which of them (is) stronger arrogant/disobedience on (to) the merciful
  19,70,"Then We are (E) more knowledgeable with (about) those who, they are more worthy/deserving roasting/suffering/burning with (in) it (Hell)"
  19,71,"And that from you (there is not) except (who is) nearing/approaching it , (that) was on (by) your Lord decidedly/positively ordered/executed"
  19,72,"Then We save/rescue those who feared and obeyed, and We leave (disregard) the unjust/oppressors in it kneeling/standing on (their) toes"
  19,73,"And when Our evidences/verses evidences are read/recited on (to) them, those who disbelieved said to those who believed: \"Which (of) the two groups/parties/flocks is (in) better residence and best gathering/assembly/club"
  19,74,And how many We destroyed from before them from people of one era/generation/century? They are better home effects/money and appearance/pleasant appearance
  19,75,"Say: \"Who was in the misguidance, so the merciful will extend/spread (E) for him extension/spreading until when they saw/understood what they are being promised, either the torture, and either the Hour/Resurrection , so they will know who he is worst (in) a place/position, and weaker soldiers/warriors"
  19,76,"And God increases those who were guided (in) guidance, and the remainders the correct/righteous deeds (are) better at your Lord a replacement/compensation and better (in) a return"
  19,77,"So did you see/understand who disbelieved with Our evidences/verses, and said: \"I will be given213property/possession/wealth and children"
  19,78,"Has he seen/been informed (of) the unseen/absent , or he took/received at the merciful a promise/contract"
  19,79,"No but, We will write/dictate what he says, and We extend/spread to him from the torture extension/spreading"
  19,80,"And We make him inherit what he says, and he comes to Us singly/alone"
  19,81,"And they took/received from other than God gods, to be for them glory/might/honour"
  19,82,"No but they will disbelieve with their worshipping, and they (are) on them adversaries/opponents"
  19,83,"Do you not see/understand that We sent the devils on (to) the disbelievers, they penetrate their minds/influence them penetration of their minds/influence"
  19,84,"So do not hurry/hasten/rush on them, but We count for them counting"
  19,85,A day We gather the fearing and obeying to the merciful (as) a delegation of dignitaries
  19,86,And We drive (herd) the criminals/sinners to Hell successively in groups
  19,87,"They do not own/possess the mediation, except who took/received at the merciful a promise/contract"
  19,88,"And they said: \"The merciful took/received a child (son)"
  19,89,You had come (with) a blasphemous/disastrous thing
  19,90,"The skies/space are about to/almost split/crack/cleave from it, and the earth/Planet Earth splits/cracks open ,and the mountains fall down (in) demolition and breaking down into pieces violently with noise"
  19,91,That (E) they called to the merciful a child (son)
  19,92,And (it) would not (be) to the merciful that He takes a child (son)
  19,93,That every/each whom (is) in the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth except is coming (E) (to) the merciful (as) a worshipper/slave
  19,94,He had counted/completed them and He counted them counting
  19,95,And all of them are coming to Him (in) the Resurrection Day singly/alone/one
  19,96,"That those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, the merciful will make/create for them love/affection"
  19,97,"So but We eased it with your tongue/language, to announce good news with it (to) the fearing and obeying, and warn/give notice with it (to) a nation (in) harsh/violent dispute"
  19,98,"And how many before them We destroyed from people of one era/generation/century, do you sense/feel from them from anyone, or hear for them (a) low voice/whisper/faint sound"